<li id="cite_note-Pontifical_Biblical_Commission--Interpretation_of_the_Bible-2">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Pontifical_Biblical_Commission--Interpretation_of_the_Bible_2-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Pontifical_Biblical_Commission--Interpretation_of_the_Bible_2-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFPresented_by_the_Pontifical_Biblical_Commission1993">Presented by the Pontifical Biblical Commission (1993-04-23). <a href="http://catholic-resources.org/ChurchDocs/PBC_Interp5.htm" class="external text" title="http://catholic-resources.org/ChurchDocs/PBC_Interp5.htm" rel="nofollow">"The Interpretation of the Bible in the Church"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://catholic-resources.org/ChurchDocs/PBC_Interp5.htm" class="external free" title="http://catholic-resources.org/ChurchDocs/PBC_Interp5.htm" rel="nofollow">http://catholic-resources.org/ChurchDocs/PBC_Interp5.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-05-21</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Interpretation+of+the+Bible+in+the+Church&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Presented+by+the+Pontifical+Biblical+Commission&amp;rft.au=Presented+by+the+Pontifical+Biblical+Commission&amp;rft.date=1993-04-23&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcatholic-resources.org%2FChurchDocs%2FPBC_Interp5.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Biblical_hermeneutics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFGrudem">Grudem, Wayne. <a href="http://www.cbmw.org/Resources/Book-Reviews/A-Redemptive-Movement-Hermeneutic-and-Gender-Equality-and-Homosexuality-by-William-J-Webb-from-Discovering-Biblical-Equality" class="external text" title="http://www.cbmw.org/Resources/Book-Reviews/A-Redemptive-Movement-Hermeneutic-and-Gender-Equality-and-Homosexuality-by-William-J-Webb-from-Discovering-Biblical-Equality" rel="nofollow">"Review of "A Redemptive-Movement Hermeneutic" and "Gender Equality and Homosexuality" by William J. Webb"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Council_on_Biblical_Manhood_and_Womanhood" title="Council on Biblical Manhood and Womanhood">Council on Biblical Manhood and Womanhood</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cbmw.org/Resources/Book-Reviews/A-Redemptive-Movement-Hermeneutic-and-Gender-Equality-and-Homosexuality-by-William-J-Webb-from-Discovering-Biblical-Equality" class="external free" title="http://www.cbmw.org/Resources/Book-Reviews/A-Redemptive-Movement-Hermeneutic-and-Gender-Equality-and-Homosexuality-by-William-J-Webb-from-Discovering-Biblical-Equality" rel="nofollow">http://www.cbmw.org/Resources/Book-Reviews/A-Redemptive-Movement-Hermeneutic-and-Gender-Equality-and-Homosexuality-by-William-J-Webb-from-Discovering-Biblical-Equality</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-10-06</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Review+of+%22A+Redemptive-Movement+Hermeneutic%22+and+%22Gender+Equality+and+Homosexuality%22+by+William+J.+Webb&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Grudem&amp;rft.aufirst=Wayne&amp;rft.au=Grudem%2C+Wayne&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BCouncil+on+Biblical+Manhood+and+Womanhood%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbmw.org%2FResources%2FBook-Reviews%2FA-Redemptive-Movement-Hermeneutic-and-Gender-Equality-and-Homo